  "template_text": "{{salutation}}\n\n[{{labels.hook}}]\n{{hook_paragraph}}\n\n[{{labels.insight}}]\n{{insight_paragraph}}\n\n[{{labels.apply}}]\n{{apply_paragraph}}\n\n— {{labels.cta}} —\n{{cta.title}}\n일시: {{cta.dates}}\n장소: {{cta.place}}\n대상: {{cta.audience_joined}}\n비용: {{cta.price}} (혜택: {{cta.perks_joined}} / 할인: {{cta.discount}})",

